     <h1>什么时候是最佳的外汇交易时间？</h1> 
    </div> 
   </div> 
  </div> 
 </div> 
 <div class="intro text_ig parbase"> 
  <p>本文将分析外汇交易者需要如何看待一天中的各个时间段以及各时段的不同之处。</p> 
 </div> 
 <div class="publication-date">
  Tuesday 05 December 2017
 </div> 
 <div class="article_intro"> 
  <div class="newspar2 parsys"> 
  </div> 
  <div class="textimage parbase"> 
   <div class="left_image image"> 
    <div class="image_border"> 
     <amp-img on="tap:lightbox42b9dc15-be78-40e0-9f55-a25da5125881" role="button" tabindex="0" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/12/05/when-is-the-best-time-of-the-day-to-trade-forex-40997/jcr:content/textimage/image.webimg.jpg/1512461684944.jpg" width="400" height="300" title="image" alt="image" layout="responsive"></amp-img> 
     <amp-image-lightbox id="lightbox42b9dc15-be78-40e0-9f55-a25da5125881" layout="nodisplay"></amp-image-lightbox> 
